PEANUT BUTTER'S POPULARITY SPREADING ACROSS THE U.S. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was so happy to read your article about the spreading popularity of peanut 
butter ("Peanut Butter Obsession Spreading Across Country," by David Treadwell, 
Part I, May 30). Now that it is no longer considered kid stuff, millions of 
adult peanut butter fanatics like myself can finally come out of the closet and 
reclaim this wholesome and delicious stuff for ourselves. 
</P>
<P>
We will know we have made it to the big time when the supermarkets decide to 
take peanut butter out of the potato chip aisle, and instead stock it on the 
shelf next to the oat bran! 
