</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ARMY TROOPS FIRE ON BEIJING CROWDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Before we get too smug and self-righteous about China, we might remember that 
it was the National Guard that fired on the students of Kent State. Only the 
number of casualties differs. 
</P>
<P>
MARGARET FOOTT 
</P>
<P>
San Diego 
</P>
</TEXT>
