<TEXT>
<P>
Shouldn't your headline have been "Les Mormons Attack Prejudice With 
Prejudice"? 
</P>
<P>
Because of the Mormon Church's legitimate rejection of homosexual activity, 
these "artists" condemn it. 
</P>
<P>
What happened to freedom of religion, or is that only for the dissidents while 
the faithful are forced to abandon what they believe? Is the "intolerance" Les 
Mormons derogate any different from the intolerance they practice? 
</P>
<P>
JOHN ARNERICH 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
