WHEELCHAIR GAMES TO BE HELD NEXT WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The ninth National Veterans Wheelchair Games, with more than 500 wheelchair 
athletes expected to compete, will be held Tuesday through next Saturday at Cal 
State Long Beach. 
</P>
<P>
The events include track and field, swimming, archery, basketball, billiards, 
bowling, slalom, table tennis, weightlifting and a motorized wheelchair rally. 
</P>
<P>
