CENTER; HOSPITALS -- FINANCES; HOSPITALS -- OVERCROWDING; BIRTHS; PATIENTS; 
INDIGENTS; HOSPITALS -- ORANGE COUNTY; AMI MEDICAL CENTER; MEDICAL CARE -- 
ORANGE COUNTY; MEDI CAL 
</P>
