European antiques and prices them in line with the dollar's strength. RICK 
PERRY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, This North Hollywood import store keeps 
buyers informed with up-to-date exchange rates. ; Photo, David Sakol, Dansk 
Mobel Export president, says prices are lower: "Our prices have dropped 19% 
since November, 1987." LACEY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
