<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALTERNATIVE THEATRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am writing to commend Jan Herman on his coverage of the financial 
difficulties that the Alternative Repertory Theatre of Santa Ana is having. 
</P>
<P>
Having seen every production that ART has mounted, I know what a cultural 
resource this theater company is becoming. Orange County needs this company's 
survival. It is gratifying to see The Times be so supportive of ART's 
endeavors. 
</P>
<P>
I would encourage all of your readers to come and see what is happening at this 
intimate theater in Santa Ana. It is well worth the time and effort. 
</P>
<P>
LORETTA BEAUMONT 
</P>
<P>
Anaheim 
</P>
</TEXT>
